  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <lg xml:id="TolC429">
  <l>avaitām,</l>
	<l>tattaṅ kiḷavi yaṭukkuna variṉu</l>
	<l>mettiṟat tāṉum peyarmuṭi piṉavē.</l>
      </lg>
    </body>
  </text>

  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/211/mode/1up">211</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/212/mode/1up">212</ref>.</p>
<p>iccūttiram eṉnutaliṟṟō veṉiṉ, itu muṟṟuccol eṉṟu mēṟkūṟappaṭṭaṉavaṟṟiṟku muṭipukūṟutal nutaliṟṟu.</p>
<p>urai : mēṟ collappaṭṭa muṟṟuc coṟkaṭām ettuṇaic collaiyum aṭukkip palavāyvariṉum peyar koṇṭu muṭital ilakkaṇattaṉa eṉṟavāṟu.</p>
<p>varalāṟu : 'uṇṭāṉ, tiṉṟāṉ, ōṭiṉāṉ, pāṭiṉāṉ cāttaṉ' eṉa varum ; itu viṉai.</p>
<p>'nallaṟivuṭaiyaṉ, cevviyaṉ, cāṉṟār makaṉ' eṉavum varum ; itu viṉaikkuṟippu.</p>
<p>maṟṟu, 'ettiṟattāṉum' eṉṟatu eṉṉai yeṉiṉ, uṇṭāṉ cāttaṉ eṉpatu peyarai muṉṉaṭuttu, cāttaṉ uṇṭāṉ eṉpatu peyaraip piṉṉaṭuttu varum eṉpatu aṟivittaṟku, 'ettiṟattāṉum' eṉṟāṟ eṉpatu. piṟavuñ collupa ; muṉṉumuriya muṟṟuc colleṉa eṉpatu.	(33)</p>
    </body>
  </text>

